---
globs: *.tsx,*.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

# Use SWR for fetches and mutations
No exceptions. When writing a SWR hook that does not exist yet, put it under `/hooks/data` e.g. `/hooks/data/useMyResource.ts`

# Use Prettier for code formatting
After you finish writing code, run `pnpm run format` which runs prettier under the hood to format the code. If you need to run it for a list of files, use `pnpm run format:paths -- app/foo.tsx`.

# Style guides
- use a multiple of 4 for paddings and margins. For example, 4px, 8px, 12px, 16px etc.